  20 Jun 2015; wjn <wjn@aol.jp> source-han-sans-jp-1.004.ebuild:
  media-fonts/{noto*,source-han-sans*}: Modify ${DOCs} to list from array.

    font.eclass supports space-delimited listed ${DOCS} only,
   though EAPI(>=4) can treat arrayed ${DOCS}.
    Therefore, space-delimited list (not array) makes codes shorter,
   because src_install can be left as default spec of font.eclass.

